data.description: Welcome to this 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home located in the city of Moreno Valley. As you walk in to this home you are greeted by the open living room with a gas fireplace. The kitchen offers granite countertops, a center island and space for a dining room table. Off the kitchen you have access to the powder room, and laundry room which has entry to the 2 car garage. Upstairs you will find 2 bedrooms, full bathroom and the Master suite. The Master suite offers a his and hers sink with granite countertops. The backyard is a blank slate to make your own! Great opportunity to own this perfect family home!   ~ Must See!!! ~
